dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents parcels for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2008. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, “Rock_Parcels_2008.gdb”. [Parcel Boundaries within Rock County.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Computerized Mapping within the Rock County GIS Geographic Information System.]
